recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Chili
recipes.description: Hearty chili cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 1 lb ground beef, 2 cans beans, 3 cans tomatoes, 2 tbsp chili powder
recipes.steps: Combine all ingredients in a Dutch oven, cook over campfire coals for 1-2 hours.

recipes.title: Campfire Pizza
recipes.description: Delicious pizza cooked in a Dutch oven over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: 1 package pizza dough, 1 cup tomato sauce, 2 cups cheese, toppings of your choice
recipes.steps: Roll out pizza dough, add sauce, top with cheese, add toppings of your choice, Cook in a preheated Dutch oven over campfire until the crust is golden.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Peach Cobbler
recipes.description: Sweet peach cobbler baked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 4 peaches, 1 cup sugar, 1.5 cups flour, 0.5 cup butter, 1 tsp cinnamon
recipes.steps: Mix peaches sugar and cinnamon in a Dutch oven, layer peaches and cover with a mixture of flour sugar and butter, Cook in the campfire coals until bubbly and golden brown.

recipes.title: Campfire Grilled Chicken Skewers
recipes.description: Flavorful chicken skewers grilled over a campfire for the perfect outdoor meal.
recipes.ingredients: 1 lb chicken breast, bell peppers, onions, olive oil, salt, pepper
recipes.steps: Marinate chicken in olive oil salt and pepper, Skewer chicken with bell peppers and onions, Grill over the campfire until chicken is cooked through

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Bacon and Cheese Campfire Potatoes
recipes.description: Savory bacon and cheese potatoes cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 4 potatoes, 1 cup shredded cheese, 6 slices bacon, green onions
recipes.steps: Slice potatoes and layer in a Dutch oven, Top with shredded cheese and bacon, Cook over campfire coals until potatoes are tender and bacon is crispy, Garnish with chopped green onions

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Breakfast Burritos
recipes.description: Hearty breakfast burritos cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 8 eggs, sausage, tortillas, cheese, salsa
recipes.steps: Scramble eggs in Dutch oven, Set eggs aside, Cook the sausage in the dutch oven, Once sausage is cooked add eggs back in, Assemble burritos with egg and sausage mixture, Top with cheese and salsa, Warm in the Dutch oven over campfire coals

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Jambalaya
recipes.description: Spicy and flavorful jambalaya cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 1 lb Andouille sausage, 1 lb chicken thighs, 1 onion, 1 bell pepper, 2 celery stalks, 2 cups rice, 3 cups chicken broth, Cajun seasoning
recipes.steps: Brown sausage and chicken in the Dutch oven, add chopped vegetables, stir in rice and broth, season with Cajun spices, cover and simmer over campfire until rice is cooked.

recipes.title: Campfire Veggie Skewers with Herb Marinade
recipes.description: Colorful vegetable skewers with a flavorful herb marinade, grilled to perfection over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Bell peppers, cherry tomatoes, zucchini, mushrooms, red onion, olive oil, garlic, rosemary, thyme, salt, pepper
recipes.steps: Thread vegetables onto skewers, mix olive oil, minced garlic, and chopped herbs for the marinade, grill skewers over campfire until veggies are tender.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Cornbread
recipes.description: Moist and golden cornbread baked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 1 cup cornmeal, 1 cup all-purpose flour, 1 tbsp baking powder, 1/2 tsp salt, 1 cup milk, 1/4 cup melted butter, 1/4 cup honey
recipes.steps: Mix dry ingredients, add milk, melted butter, and honey, stir until just combined, pour into greased Dutch oven, bake over campfire until a toothpick comes out clean.

recipes.title: Campfire Quesadillas
recipes.description: Cheesy and satisfying quesadillas cooked in a cast iron skillet over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Flour tortillas, shredded cheese, cooked chicken or beef, bell peppers, onions, salsa, sour cream
recipes.steps: Place tortilla in a hot skillet, add cheese, meat, veggies, and another layer of cheese, top with another tortilla, cook on both sides until cheese is melted.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Lasagna
recipes.description: Layers of pasta, meat sauce, and cheese baked to perfection in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: Lasagna noodles, ground beef, marinara sauce, ricotta cheese, mozzarella cheese, Parmesan cheese, Italian seasoning
recipes.steps: Brown beef in Dutch oven, add marinara sauce and seasoning, layer noodles and cheese, repeat, cover and cook over campfire until noodles are tender.

recipes.title: Campfire Garlic Butter Shrimp
recipes.description: Succulent shrimp marinated in garlic butter and grilled over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Shrimp, garlic, melted butter, lemon juice, parsley, salt, pepper
recipes.steps: Combine melted butter, minced garlic, lemon juice, and chopped parsley, marinate shrimp, skewer and grill over campfire until shrimp are pink and opaque.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Mac and Cheese
recipes.description: Creamy and cheesy macaroni and cheese cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: Elbow macaroni, cheddar cheese, milk, butter, flour, salt, pepper
recipes.steps: Cook macaroni in the Dutch oven, make a roux with butter and flour, add milk and cheese, stir in cooked macaroni, cook until cheese is melted and bubbly.

recipes.title: Campfire Sausage and Veggie Foil Packets
recipes.description: Easy and customizable foil packets with sausages and veggies, cooked over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Sausages, potatoes, carrots, bell peppers, onions, olive oil, garlic, herbs, salt, pepper
recipes.steps: Chop ingredients, place on a foil sheet, drizzle with olive oil, add minced garlic and herbs, seal the foil packets, cook over campfire until veggies are tender.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Apple and Cinnamon Breakfast Rolls
recipes.description: Sweet and gooey cinnamon rolls with apple filling, baked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: Refrigerated cinnamon roll dough, apples, brown sugar, cinnamon, butter
recipes.steps: Roll out cinnamon roll dough, spread with apple mixture, roll up and slice into rolls, place in greased Dutch oven, bake over campfire until golden.

recipes.title: Campfire Banana S'mores
recipes.description: A twist on classic s'mores with banana slices, grilled to perfection over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Graham crackers, chocolate bars, marshmallows, bananas
recipes.steps: Place banana slices on graham crackers, top with chocolate and marshmallow, sandwich with another cracker, grill over campfire until marshmallow is gooey and chocolate is melted.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Enchiladas
recipes.description: Flavorful enchiladas cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: 1 lb ground beef, 1 onion, 1 can black beans, 1 can enchilada sauce, tortillas, shredded cheese
recipes.steps: Brown beef and onions in the Dutch oven, add beans and enchilada sauce, fill tortillas and roll them up, top with cheese, cook until cheese is melted.

recipes.title: Campfire Shrimp Boil
recipes.description: Classic shrimp boil with potatoes, corn, and sausage, cooked over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Shrimp, potatoes, corn on the cob, smoked sausage, Old Bay seasoning, lemons
recipes.steps: Boil water in a large pot or Dutch oven, add Old Bay seasoning, potatoes, corn, and sausage, cook until potatoes are tender, add shrimp and cook until pink, serve with lemon wedges.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Paella
recipes.description: A Spanish-inspired paella cooked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: Chicken thighs, chorizo, shrimp, rice, saffron, chicken broth, bell peppers, peas
recipes.steps: Brown chicken and chorizo in the Dutch oven, add rice, saffron, and broth, arrange shrimp and vegetables on top, cover and simmer over campfire until rice is cooked.

recipes.title: Campfire Sweet Potato and Black Bean Tacos
recipes.description: Vegetarian tacos with roasted sweet potatoes and black beans, cooked over a campfire.
recipes.ingredients: Sweet potatoes, black beans, taco seasoning, tortillas, salsa, avocado
recipes.steps: Roast sweet potatoes in the Dutch oven, add black beans and taco seasoning, warm tortillas and assemble tacos, top with salsa and avocado.

recipes.title: Dutch Oven Campfire Lemon Blueberry Cake
recipes.description: Moist and flavorful lemon blueberry cake baked in a Dutch oven over campfire coals.
recipes.ingredients: Flour, sugar, baking powder, salt, butter, eggs, milk, lemon zest, blueberries
recipes.steps: Mix dry ingredients, add wet ingredients and fold in blueberries, pour into a greased Dutch oven, bake over campfire coals until a toothpick comes out clean.
